        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac {\\sqrt{2}(\\cos (\\pi/12) + i \\sin\n(\\pi/12))}{1+i} = \\frac {\\sqrt{3}-i}{2}.\\)</span></p>\n"
